Class Messages

java.lang.Object
com.bws.jdistil.core.message.Messages
public class Messages extends Object
Class defining message constants used to retrieve messages from the messages resource bundle.

  • Method Details

    • formatMessage

      public static String formatMessage(Locale locale, String messageKey, Object value)
      Returns a formatted standard predefined message.  The detailKey is used to retrieve a standard predefined message that is formatted using information supplied in the value parameter.  Provided for convience when using standard messages requiring only one value parameter.
      Parameters:
      locale - - Locale.
      messageKey - - Key used to retrieve a standard predefined message.
      value - - Value used to format a standard predefined message.
      Returns:
      String - Formatted standard predefined message.
      See Also:
      • MessageResource

    • formatMessage

      public static String formatMessage(Locale locale, String type, Object[] values)
      Returns a formatted standard predefined message. The detailKey is used to retrieve a standard predefined message that is formatted using information supplied in the values parameter.
      Parameters:
      locale - - Locale.
      type - - Message type used to retrieve a standard predefined message.
      values - - Array of values used to format a standard predefined message.
      Returns:
      String - Formatted standard predefined message.
      See Also:
      • MessageResource

    • getMessage

      public static String getMessage(String type, Locale locale)
      Returns a locale specific message for a given message type.
      Parameters:
      type - Message type.
      locale - Target locale.
      Returns:
      String Locale specific message.
